        {
          "html": "<style>\n  :root {\n    --color-pitch-black: #000000;\n    --color-pure-white: #ffffff;\n    --color-faint-gray: #e5e5e5;\n    --font-abc-oracle: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    --spacing-6: 6px;\n    --spacing-8: 8px;\n    --spacing-12: 12px;\n    --spacing-48: 48px;\n  }\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap');\n\n  .about-section {\n    background: var(--color-pure-white);\n    width: 600px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: var(--spacing-48) var(--spacing-12);\n    font-family: var(--font-abc-oracle);\n  }\n\n  .about-text-block {\n    max-width: 380px;\n  }\n\n  .about-body {\n    color: var(--color-pitch-black);\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-family: var(--font-abc-oracle);\n    line-height: 1.43;\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n\n  .about-tagline {\n    color: var(--color-pitch-black);\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-family: var(--font-abc-oracle);\n    line-height: 1.43;\n    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-48) 0;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n\n  .btn-primary {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: var(--color-pitch-black);\n    color: var(--color-pure-white);\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-family: var(--font-abc-oracle);\n    line-height: 1;\n    padding: var(--spacing-8) var(--spacing-12);\n    border-radius: 9999px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--color-pitch-black);\n    text-decoration: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n\n  .btn-primary:hover {\n    background: var(--color-pure-white);\n    color: var(--color-pitch-black);\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"about-section\">\n  <div class=\"about-text-block\">\n    <p class=\"about-body\">I design digital products and websites with a focus on clarity and structure. For me, design is a dialogue between users, designers, and developers—where strategy and aesthetics work together to create something that feels effortless.</p>\n    <p class=\"about-tagline\">Subtle, but with great impact.</p>\n    <a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"#\">Information</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
